OL,3,CWaterfall deaths ruled accidental as
OL,4,Ccoroner raises safety concerns
OL,6,FAn inquest into the deaths of three
OL,7,Fpeople at a popular waterfall beauty
OL,8,Fspot in south Wales has concluded all
OL,9,Fthree were accidental.
OL,11,FThe hearing at Pontypridd Coroner's
OL,12,FCourt examined the deaths of Corey
OL,13,FLongdon, 26, who fell while walking in
OL,14,Fthe area in June 2024, and Rachael and
OL,15,FHelen Patching, a married couple from
OL,16,FWest Malling who drowned while on
OL,17,Fholiday in January 2023.
