OL,3,CWaterfall deaths ruled accidental as
OL,4,Ccoroner raises safety concerns
OL,6,FAll three deaths happened in the
OL,7,Fwaterfalls area near Ystradfellte in
OL,8,Fthe Brecon Beacons National Park, now
OL,9,Fknown as Bannau Brycheiniog.
OL,11,FCoroner for South Wales Central,
OL,12,FPatricia Morgan, concluded that in all
OL,13,Fcases the deaths were accidental, but
OL,14,Fsaid she will now issue a formal
OL,15,FPrevention of Future Deaths Report,
OL,16,Fraising concerns about safety,
OL,17,Fsignage, path access and poor mobile
OL,18,Fphone signal in the area.
