OL,3,CWaterfall deaths ruled accidental as
OL,4,Ccoroner raises safety concerns
OL,6,FThe coroner found it was "more likely
OL,7,Fthan not" that Helen, 52, and Rachael,
OL,8,F33, were well-equipped and hiking in
OL,9,FWaterfall Country on 4 January 2023,
OL,10,Fand were not attempting wild swimming.
OL,12,FShe said there was insufficient
OL,13,Fevidence to determine the exact point
OL,14,Fat which either woman entered the
OL,15,Fwater near Sgwd Yr Pannwr waterfall,
OL,16,Fbut concluded it was more likely than
OL,17,Fnot one entered the water accidentally
OL,18,Fand the other attempted a rescue.
