OL,3,CWaterfall deaths ruled accidental as
OL,4,Ccoroner raises safety concerns
OL,6,FThe coroner said the fact their shoes
OL,7,Fwere not left behind suggested urgency
OL,8,Fand that the incident was "entirely
OL,9,Funintended".
OL,11,FHelen Patching's body was recovered
OL,12,Ffrom the water on 6 January. Rachael
OL,13,FPatching's body was found on 8 January
OL,14,Fseveral miles downstream in the River
OL,15,FNeath near Spring Lakes campsite.
OL,17,FIn both cases, the medical cause of
OL,18,Fdeath was recorded as drowning and the
OL,19,Fformal conclusion was accidental death.
