OL,3,CWaterfall deaths ruled accidental as
OL,4,Ccoroner raises safety concerns
OL,6,FRachael and Helen's family have
OL,7,Fpreviously described them as a devoted
OL,8,Fand selfless couple who loved the
OL,9,Foutdoors and animals.
OL,11,FThe inquest heard Corey Longdon had
OL,12,Fbeen visiting the area with his aunt
OL,13,Fon a camping trip on 26 June 2024.
OL,15,FThe coroner found it was more likely
OL,16,Fthan not that he left a path in search
OL,17,Fof a shortcut to a waterfall and fell
OL,18,Fdown a steep incline into the water
OL,19,Fbelow.
