OL,3,CWaterfall deaths ruled accidental as
OL,4,Ccoroner raises safety concerns
OL,6,FThe fall was partially witnessed.
OL,7,FCorey suffered catastrophic head
OL,8,Finjuries and went into traumatic
OL,9,Fcardiac arrest at the scene.
OL,11,FTwo air ambulances attended and he was
OL,12,Fflown to the University Hospital of
OL,13,FWales in Cardiff, where life support
OL,14,Fwas later withdrawn. He died at around
OL,15,F11:30pm that evening.
OL,17,FHis medical cause of death was
OL,18,Frecorded as:
OL,20,FThe formal conclusion was accidental
OL,21,Fdeath.
