OL,3,CWaterfall deaths ruled accidental as
OL,4,Ccoroner raises safety concerns
OL,6,FOne of the key witnesses at the
OL,7,Finquest was Andrew Lamb, a mountain
OL,8,Fleader and outdoor safety campaigner
OL,9,Fwith more than 30 years' experience in
OL,10,Fthe waterfalls area.
OL,12,FIn a detailed statement, he told the
OL,13,Fcourt he had repeatedly warned both
OL,14,FNatural Resources Wales and the
OL,15,FNational Park Authority since 2021
OL,16,Fthat the closure of a footpath linking
OL,17,Fthe Clun Gwyn waterfalls had created
OL,18,Fconfusion for walkers and led to
OL,19,Fpeople following unsafe unofficial
OL,20,Froutes, known as "desire lines".
