OL,3,CWaterfall deaths ruled accidental as
OL,4,Ccoroner raises safety concerns
OL,6,FHe said he had warned that without
OL,7,Fclearer signage and a managed
OL,8,Falternative route, accidents and
OL,9,Fdeaths would occur at the location
OL,10,Fwhere Corey later fell.
OL,12,FMr Lamb told the court he was
OL,13,Ffrustrated that significant changes,
OL,14,Fincluding fencing, were only
OL,15,Fintroduced after the most recent death.
OL,17,FAlthough the coroner said there is now
OL,18,Fclear signage warning of water dangers
OL,19,Fat the waterfalls, she said new issues
OL,20,Fhave emerged which require action.
