OL,3,CWaterfall deaths ruled accidental as
OL,4,Ccoroner raises safety concerns
OL,6,FShe raised concerns about:
OL,8,FShe said she was pleased to hear work
OL,9,Fis under way to address some inherent
OL,10,Fdangers at one of the waterfall
OL,11,Fviewing points, which is aimed to be
OL,12,Fcompleted by Easter.
OL,14,FFor those reasons, she confirmed she
OL,15,Fwill issue a Regulation 28 Prevention
OL,16,Fof Future Deaths Report to Natural
OL,17,FResources Wales, Bannau Brycheiniog
OL,18,FNational Park Authority and the
OL,19,Frelevant local authorities. They will
OL,20,Fhave 120 days to respond.
