OL,6,FCatherine Mealing-Jones, chief
OL,7,Fexecutive of Bannau Brycheiniog
OL,8,FNational Park Authority (BBNPA), said
OL,9,Fboth signage and social media channels
OL,10,Fare used to raise awareness of safety
OL,11,Fissues.
OL,13,FShe said she was "satisfied" the most
OL,14,Fcommon access points to the trail have
OL,15,Fthe correct signage and warned other
OL,16,Fmeasures, such as lifebuoy rings,
OL,17,Fcould cause additional dangers in the
OL,18,Fwater or encourage people to swim.
