OL,6,FSamuel Jones, representing Natural
OL,7,FResources Wales (NRW), said there had
OL,8,Fbeen "significant investment, new
OL,9,Froutes and fencing" put in place near
OL,10,Fthe site of Mr Longdon's fall in an
OL,11,Feffort to improve safety.
OL,13,F"These organisations do take their
OL,14,Fresponsibilities very seriously and
OL,15,Fthey have to balance their
OL,16,Fresponsibilities with the need to
OL,17,Fpreserve the environment in these
OL,18,Flocations," he added.
